# Keep the Docker build context small AND eunsure host-built (macOS) artifacts never leak into the linux omages. Everything below is regenerated inside the image by `pnpm install` / `nest build` / `next build`
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
.git
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Local env + editor/OS cruft. (All .env files - runtime env comes from compose, never baked into the image; also keeps a locl src/apps/.env out of the image.)
.env
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
*DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Docs / non-build assets
**/*.md
*.pdf